Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not about to be stranded\Nby something such as rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are leaving, Sophia Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dark barrier renders \Nall attacks ineffective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Don't think about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about him. Don't think about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is emotional turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The angel must be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I still have my power.\NIt hasn't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something before it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Rikka had come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been staying out late every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's summer vacation, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya, your sticker is coming off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn you, angel! It will take more\Nthan these cheap illusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to faze this magical girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been getting enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you out so late yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:32.97,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE X GAUNTLET OF RAIN [OR]\NA MIDSUMMER NIGHT'S... RAIN AND WHIPS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I have told you many times,\Nto speak it means death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock that off or you're grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the proximity of the Priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you may have been mentally contaminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are even starting to look like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, no diving please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you defeat me within the water,\NWicked Lord Shingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-please, not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making weird sounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cento, we're not allowed to jump\Ninto pools in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Toka is the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget. You must forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it all disappear, in the Devil's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the profane name of the Angel Lucifer,\Nrid me of my memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not working!\NI can hear his voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is an excellent meditation spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! As a magical devil girl,\NI meditate daily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya, your shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attacks are getting \Nmore vicious every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What got into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but I am a \Nveritable feast of rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you blithering about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Rikka and I will be at the library\Ndoing our homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, increased body temperature confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby request supplementary\Ncooling components.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Scarf gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Shichimiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, only Rikka can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't happen till nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to take turns napping?\NI brought pillows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't. The neighborhood\Nassociation director said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that if we stay here until night time,\Nthey'll pay us for our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they should put us to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand wasting time like this\Nwithout any sense of accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks to be you, Morisummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could definitely use more momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must you always insist upon\Ninterfering with my plans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask you to follow me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am compelled to send you beyond\Nthe reaches of the parallel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was feeling bored anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't hurt to play \Nalong once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am buying all of these water yo-yo's!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take this to mean you \Nwill do battle with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do battle nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to crush you without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're to blame for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Dekomori, am my master's servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will happily obey her sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you sucking up to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do something\Nabout it myself if I had the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have to head back to Italy soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MUNICIPAL LIBRARY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no intention of doing your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we did just get out of the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.36,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,INCOMING TEXT - TOKA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:08:00.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SUB: GOING BACK TO ITALY\NFind the answer for yourselves.\NContact me if there's trouble.\NThat is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right. I'm on \Nmy way back to Italy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've checked in on Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we should sit down for a meal together,\Njust the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear! My netherworld \Nbarrier is active...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so none of your attacks \Nwill affect me, Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is an extremely formidable foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.25,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU'VE GOT MAIL\NWICKED LORD SHINGAN\NUNSEAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am completely restored! \NHP/MP are topped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pumped up with magical energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier on this room is impeccable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I would expect from a magical devil girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight I will once again attempt\Nto locate the parallel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the whereabouts of\Nthe key to the Dark Flame Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still looking for the last one then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, for I am bound by contract\Nto the Dark Flame Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Wicked Lord Shingan's mission.\NOnly I can locate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl TWIRLY CURLY KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is interfering. Perhaps\Nit is the Mage Association's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...out of fear the evolution \Nof Dark Flame Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night of the blue moon\Ncould be upon us at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tricky. Why don't you ask Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he remembers something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will not hold\Nas proof of our contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you'd be punished the next time \Nyou left without saying anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I cannot say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, this is a time of \Nrepose for Dark Beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack of the Light Beings\Nis taking its toll on my barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I am so sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. You and your sordid hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What other choice do I have?\NAnd I never asked you to tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Shichimiya now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sighed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked at Togashi's apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Toka was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us if it isn't so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NI am a magical devil girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am charged with my\Neternal battle against the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not like your average human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She averted her eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you imagine the following:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are alone in a classroom with Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are alone in a movie \Ntheatre with Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are alone on a desert \Nisland with Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating Devil Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This renders any psychological \Nattack ineffective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even reacts identically to Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're in love with Togashi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in fact a marauder\Nwho showed up on this land...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to wrest Ghelzonianses away from my master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a homewrecker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-no! I'm not! Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've always had\Na thing for him, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit, there once was a period of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I experienced emotional\Ninstability towards Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was then that I made
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my decision to live my life as a \Nmagical devil girl for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that everything is resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance to the logic of the world\Nand its natural laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deko seems to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I have defeated\Nthe enemy within once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stamp it out thoroughly this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a shortcut through this park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the festival of the living dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about it like that!\NIt's the Bon Festival dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremonial dance performed\Nby a myriad of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to summon the dark follower\Nconverts to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, don't talk about it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they didn't see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I put up a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am tops when it comes to barriers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing changes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am and always will be the devilish girl\Nwho rules the magical seven holy lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it's that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am at war with myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so naturally I've factored in\Nthe personal damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha, are you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ought to do it. There, done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so cute, Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Not too tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is difficult to access my weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Schwartz Z/X Perfect\NCustomized Ghelzonianses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take that with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I must keep this on \Nmy person at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Wicked Lord Shingan, it is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. That's because\Nmy big brother gave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are so lovey dovey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow! That hurts, Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is now gone and \NI've lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I split my magic with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a job, Kuzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The neighborhood association director\Nurged me to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying they'd pay me for my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Satone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Rikka invited her to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she was too busy to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deathly ghost planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Venus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's red! Fire attributes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it can't be Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip! Fight, Sophia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a magical devil girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.28,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,COTTON CANDY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:38.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,WATER BALLOONS (1 TRY 100 YEN)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo-Yo fishing is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer is such a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is just plain noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! Your dark plumage\Ndoes justice to your dark being!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kuzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been captured by\Nthe neighborhood association.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did she bother coming\Nto the festival in a yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she finds it fun in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she finds it fun in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am magical devil girl,\NSophia Ring SP Saturn VII!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the magical devil girl Sophia\Nthe whole town is talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AKA the devilish girl who rules\Nthe magical seven holy lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't you forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did come after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my schedule opened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sensed a dark presence\Na moment ago and went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? For crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her to stay put so she\Nwouldn't mess up her yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to make war with the enemy within.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make war, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The enemy is inside me,\Nso I can't escape it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've decided to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by for my report of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely it can't have gotten this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh. Where the heck is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya. Have you seen Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I suspect she has\Nspotted a dark follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, it's really coming down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you dry enough over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I have put up a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful to give the deities\Nbehind you their space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, let's start the hostilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have entered into a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lover's contract with Wicked \NLord Shingan, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sure, sorta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done it? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have you kissed and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get angry no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I get angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, Nibutani gets angry\Nwhen I'm honest with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Morisummer \Nis mentally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I practice self-discipline, so I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I should mention that we've held hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've even touched noses thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me. This is my battle.\NPlease continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you love Wicked Lord Shingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you just drop it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you love about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I love everything about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you'll get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack was harsh. \NIts power is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one registered as critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay me no mind. I'm fighting a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me it's just embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way around \Nit, because this is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a matter of life or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still wanna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I should be able to \Nmove in for the kill soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Rikka was\Nwatching me the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She watched me and kept on believing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even after I had stopped\Nbelieving in my own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have mostly given up on it,\Nbut she keeps encouraging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said I was incredible.\NShe said I had unique power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are both you and Nibutani\Nso keen to hear stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.27,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,INCOMING TEXT - RIKKA TAKANASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:29.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The water mage's attack has intensified.\NRescue requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust her not to have her umbrella\Nwhen she needs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I'm fine \Nbecause I have my barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't accept goodbyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I successfully held back the tears!\NI am victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a formidable foe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it will take more than that \Nto shake up the rock-steady
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia the magical devil girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something you can use\Nabandoned over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a coward resorts to surprise attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,